Legal Counsel, 3+PQE, Dubai
Legal Counsel, 3+PQE, Dubai
Location:  --Dubai
This international maritime organisation operates worldwide in the oil and gas industry. The company now seeks a Legal Counsel to join the team in Dubai. The ideal candidate will be 3+PQE and have extensive contract law experience, ideally gained within the seismic, shipping or oil & gas sector. Lawyers qualified in England and Wales would be preferred, but US, Australian and New Zealand lawyers will also be considered with the relevant industry experience.
Responsibilities will include providing legal advice to internal departments on all legal matters, including advising on all legal aspects of bid proposals and tenders; assisting with negotiation on seismic contracts and advising on charter hires, ship agency agreements and other relevant contracts.
For further details, candidates fulfilling the above criteria are invited to send their CV in complete confidence to
